## Data Flow

### Sync Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant API as Flask API
    participant SE as Sync Engine
    participant AM as Apple Mail
    participant GM as Gmail API
    participant DB as SQLite
    participant AI as Gemini API

    UI->>API: POST /api/sync
    API->>SE: sync_all()
    
    par Apple Mail Sync
        SE->>AM: fetch_emails(limit)
        AM-->>SE: [email dicts]
    and Gmail Sync
        SE->>GM: fetch_emails(limit)
        GM-->>SE: [email dicts]
    end
    
    SE->>DB: Insert new emails (dedup by message_id)
    SE->>DB: Update SyncLog
    
    SE->>AI: detect_newsletters(unclassified_senders)
    AI-->>SE: classification results
    SE->>DB: Update Sender + Email tables
    
    API-->>UI: {status: "complete", new_emails: N}
```

### Reading Flow (Fully Offline)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant Flask as Flask Server
    participant DB as SQLite

    UI->>Flask: GET /inbox
    Flask->>DB: SELECT emails WHERE is_newsletter=true ORDER BY date DESC
    DB-->>Flask: [emails]
    Flask-->>UI: Rendered inbox.html

    UI->>Flask: GET /read/42
    Flask->>DB: SELECT * FROM email WHERE id=42
    DB-->>Flask: email with full HTML body
    Flask->>DB: UPDATE email SET is_read=true
    Flask-->>UI: Rendered reader.html (HTML body in sandboxed iframe)
```

